The paper deals with the problem of reading text from images, which is a common task in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed approach involves the use of deep learning techniques, which are often used in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of attention mechanisms and recurrent neural networks, which are commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR).
